=== 股價井噴 ===
2021年1月11日，遊戲驛站宣布Chewy的聯合創始人瑞安·科恩及前高管阿兰·阿塔尔（Alan Attal）、吉姆·格鲁贝（Jim Grube）加入GameStop董事会<ref>{{Cite web |date=2021-01-11 |title=GameStop Announces Additional Board Refreshment to Accelerate Transformation |url=https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2021/01/11/2156168/0/en/GameStop-Announces-Additional-Board-Refreshment-to-Accelerate-Transformation.html |access-date=2021-01-29 |website=GlobeNewswire |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129160834/https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2021/01/11/2156168/0/en/GameStop-Announces-Additional-Board-Refreshment-to-Accelerate-Transformation.html}}</ref>。投资者预期這将推动遊戲驛站转型，使股价從1月12日的收盤價19.95美元上漲至1月14日的39.91美元。1月19日，{{link-en|香櫞研究|Citron Research}}发布了对遊戲驛站的沽空报告。其创始人{{en-link|安德鲁·莱夫特|Andrew Left}}認為遊戲驛站股價被严重高估，最终会跌至20美元，還辱罵高价买入GameStop股票的散户是“蠢货”（suckers）<ref name="VergeGameStophalts" /><ref>{{Cite web |date=2021-01-22 |title=Short-seller Citron said its scheduled livestream on why GameStop buyers are 'suckers at this poker game' was halted by attempted Twitter hacks|url=https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/citron-research-livestream-gamestop-position-halted-twitter-hack-attempts-2021-1-1029993391 |access-date=2021-01-31 |website=Bussiness Insider |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127120721/https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/citron-research-livestream-gamestop-position-halted-twitter-hack-attempts-2021-1-1029993391}}</ref>。不久，WSB的用戶開始對遊戲驛站股票發動軋空，令其股價飆升<ref>{{Cite web |last=Li |first=Yun |date=2021-01-27 |title=GameStop mania explained: How the Reddit retail trading crowd ran over Wall Street pros |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/27/gamestop-mania-explained-how-the-reddit-retail-trading-crowd-ran-over-wall-street-pros.html |access-date=2021-01-27 |website=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127221220/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/27/gamestop-mania-explained-how-the-reddit-retail-trading-crowd-ran-over-wall-street-pros.html}}</ref>。至1月26日時，遊戲驛站股票已經因高換手率而多次被暫停交易<ref name="CNBCNotBackingDown" /><ref name="MarketWatchStockRockets" />。軋空使得期權的市值升高，導致發生{{link-en|伽瑪擠壓|gamma squeeze}}，空方被迫購買股票以補充其日趨減少的倉位<ref name="FoolGammaSqueeze" />。

在遊戲驛站股價與2021年1月26日上漲92.7%之後，商業大亨[[伊隆·馬斯克|伊隆·馬斯克]]發了一條推文稱「Gamestonk!!」，並附上WSB的連結<ref name="CNBCMuskTweets" />。遊戲驛站股價因馬斯克的推文而一度井噴至超過200美元<ref>{{Cite web|last=Business|first=Allison Morrow, CNN|title=Elon Musk tweet fuels frenzied GameStop surge|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/26/investing/gamestop-stock-elon-musk-reddit/index.html|access-date=2021-01-29|website=CNN|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128214736/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/26/investing/gamestop-stock-elon-musk-reddit/index.html}}</ref>。{{As of|2021|1|28}}，遊戲驛站的盤中最高價是483美元（不含盤後交易時間），是其最低價2.57美元的近190倍<ref name="GoogleFinanceGMEPrice" />。

2021年1月27日，WSB對和遊戲驛站狀況類似的[[AMC電影院|AMC電影院]]（AMC）股票發動軋空<ref name="VergeTurnsToAMC" />。股票代碼類似的[[AMC電視網|AMC電視網]]（AMCX）股價也開始飆升<ref name="TheWeekConfusedAMCX" />。多家券商公司，如[[嘉信理財集團|嘉信理財集團]]旗下的{{link-en|德美利證券|TD Ameritrade}}和[[羅賓漢_(公司)|羅賓漢]]對相關股票進行了交易限制<ref name="MarketWatchDisruptions" /><ref name="NYTLimitingTrades"/>。據[[彭博有限合夥企業|彭博社]]報道，美國股市1月27日的交易量（以股份數計算）超過了2008年10月金融危機時的峰值，並且是過去13年以來以美元計算的第三高交易量<ref name="FTRedditBattle"/>。

=== 被券商暫停買入 ===
2021年1月28日，遊戲驛站在盤前交易時間繼續走高，達到近500美元<ref name="NYSE" />。然而同一天，羅賓漢在其交易平台上撤除了遊戲驛站、AMC、黑莓、諾基亞等股票，投資者雖然可以平倉這些股票，但無法開倉<ref name="AutoFB-6"/>。其他券商亦有效仿。交易者對此極為憤怒，並在Reddit的多個討論帖上呼籲發動集體訴訟<ref name="HillRobinHoodClassAction"/>。在當天交易時間之後，羅賓漢表示將從翌日允許對相關股票進行「有限購買」，但「有限購買」的定義仍不得而知<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blog.robinhood.com/news/2021/1/28/an-update-on-market-volatility|title=An Update on Market Volatility|website=Under the Hood|access-date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128213936/https://blog.robinhood.com/news/2021/1/28/an-update-on-market-volatility}}</ref>。[[微牛證券|微牛證券]]CEO安東尼·丹尼爾（Anthony Denier）表示，他們在清算所的抵押要求被不斷提高，這意味著微牛證券本身亦被限制開倉<ref>{{Cite news|last=McCabe|first=Caitlin|date=2021-01-28|title=GameStop Trading Restrictions Blamed on Wall Street’s Clearing Firm by Online Broker|language=en-US|work=Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/gamestop-trading-restrictions-blamed-on-wall-streets-clearing-firm-by-online-broker-11611867105|access-date=2021-01-29|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129040711/https://www.wsj.com/articles/gamestop-trading-restrictions-blamed-on-wall-streets-clearing-firm-by-online-broker-11611867105}}</ref>。英國的Trading212、以色列的eToro等交易平台雖然允許售出遊戲驛站和相關公司股票，但禁止買入<ref name="Auto9F-2"/>。[[微牛證券|微牛證券]]一度暫停購入訂單<ref>{{cite web|last1=Crowley|first1=James|date=2021-01-28|title=Webull follows Robinhood in blocking GameStop, AMC trades after being suggested as alternate trading platform|url=https://www.newsweek.com/webull-blocks-gamestop-amc-transactions-stock-market-robinhood-1565172|website=Newsweek|language=en|access-date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128172109/https://www.newsweek.com/webull-blocks-gamestop-amc-transactions-stock-market-robinhood-1565172}}</ref>，但很快又恢復交易<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2020-01-28|title=UPDATE: GME, AMC, and KOSS are no longer restricted.|url=https://twitter.com/WebullGlobal/status/1354875836810342400|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129040716/https://pbs.twimg.com/hashflag/config-2021-01-29-04.json|archive-date=2021-01-29|access-date=|website=Twitter}}</ref>。有用戶稱羅賓漢未經許可擅自售出他們持有的股票，但羅賓漢否認這一指控<ref>{{citeweb |title=Robinhood denies claims that it sold GameStop shares out from under its traders |url=https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/28/22254857/robinhood-gamestop-amc-shares-sold-surprised-users |first=Jacob |last=Kastrenakes |date=2021-01-28 |work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129012844/https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/28/22254857/robinhood-gamestop-amc-shares-sold-surprised-users}}</ref>。

包括羅賓漢在內的數家券商資1月29日稱，交易限制是因{{link-en|清算所|Clearing house (finance)}}徵集了執行交易所需的[[擔保物權|擔保物權]]導致<ref name="FT 210129">{{cite news |last1=Mackenzie |first1=Michael |display-authors=etal |title=Robinhood raises $1bn from investors and taps banks at end of wild week |url=https://www.ft.com/content/9a1b24e6-0433-462a-a860-c2504ea565e4 |access-date=2021-01-29 |work=[[Financial_Times|Financial Times]] |date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129005126/https://www.ft.com/content/9a1b24e6-0433-462a-a860-c2504ea565e4}}</ref><ref name="WSJ 210129">{{cite news |last1=Rudegeair |first1=Peter |title=Robinhood Raises $1 Billion to Meet Surging Cash Demands |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/robinhood-raises-1-billion-to-meet-surging-cash-demands-11611928504?page=1 |access-date=2021-01-29 |work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] |date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130044554/https://www.wsj.com/articles/robinhood-raises-1-billion-to-meet-surging-cash-demands-11611928504?page=1}}</ref><ref name="Bloom 210129">{{cite news |last1=Massa |first1=Annie |display-authors=etal |title=Robinhood Fallout Sweeps Market After $1 Billion Lifeline |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-29/for-robinhood-a-dash-for-cash-after-traders-took-on-wall-street |access-date=2021-01-29 |work=[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]]|date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129082101/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-29/for-robinhood-a-dash-for-cash-after-traders-took-on-wall-street}}</ref>。由於投資者從購買股票到兌換現金之間存在時間差，因此券商必須在清算所過賬擔保物權，以確保投資者訂單正確結算<ref name="WSJ 210129" />。涉及的清算所包括處理股票的DTCC（Depository Trust & Clearing Corporation），以及處理期權的OCC（Options Clearing Corporation）<ref name="FT 210129" />。券商稱由於無法及時提供因股價上漲而增加的擔保物權，因此必須暫停交易<ref name="FT 210129" /><ref name="WSJ 210129" /><ref name="Bloom 210129" />。例如DTCC的擔保物權總要求從260億美元增加到335億美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://archive.md/20210129171738/https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2021-01-29/reddit-traders-on-robinhood-are-on-both-sides-of-gamestop|title=GameStop Stock Game Got Stomped|access-date=2021-01-29|last=Levine|first=Matt|website=[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]]|date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130044530/http://archive.md/20210129171738/https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2021-01-29/reddit-traders-on-robinhood-are-on-both-sides-of-gamestop}}</ref><ref name="FT 210129B">{{cite news |last1=Mackenzie |first1=Michael |display-authors=etal |title=Robinhood tightens GameStop trading curbs again as SEC weighs in |url=https://www.ft.com/content/c5a85213-ca41-438d-9087-ff78791eabff |access-date=2021-01-30 |work=[[Financial_Times|Financial Times]] |date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129204349/https://www.ft.com/content/c5a85213-ca41-438d-9087-ff78791eabff}}</ref>。清算所指出特定股票的大量交易對公司造成巨大風險，特別是如果結算方集中在市場一側<ref name="FT 210129B" />。據1月29日報道，羅賓漢籌集了10億美元，以使公司免受特定股票利息增加導致的財務壓力，並滿足清算所的擔保物權要求<ref name="NYT 210129">{{cite news |last1=Kelly |first1=Kate |display-authors=etal |title=Robinhood, in Need of Cash, Raises $1 Billion From Its Investors |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/29/technology/robinhood-fundraising.html |access-date=2021-01-29 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129055625/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/29/technology/robinhood-fundraising.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Egan|first=Matt|title=Robinhood gets $1 billion infusion, signaling cash crunch|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/29/investing/robinhood-gamestop-reddit/index.html|access-date=2021-01-29|website=[[CNN|CNN]]|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129132059/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/29/investing/robinhood-gamestop-reddit/index.html}}</ref>。

截止2021年1月29日，羅賓漢仍然對遊戲驛站、AMC和黑莓的股票進行交易限制<ref name="FT 210129B" />。1月30日，羅賓漢表示其限制交易的股票種類從13個增加到50個，包括[[勞斯萊斯汽車|勞斯萊斯汽車]]和[[星巴克|星巴克]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.foxbusiness.com/markets/robinhood-expands-trading-restrictions |title=Robinhood expands trading restrictions to 50 stocks |date=2021-01-30 |last=Conklin |first=Audrey |website=Fox Business |access-date=2021-01-31}}</ref>。但1月31日，羅賓漢表示已解除部分限制，並且僅限制賣出8種股票<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-31/robinhood-narrows-trading-restrictions-to-8-companies-from-50 |title=Robinhood Narrows Trading Restrictions to Eight Companies |date=2021-01-31 |last=Yang |first=Yueqi |website=Bloomberg News |access-date=2021-01-31}}</ref>。
=== 市值下跌 ===
遊戲驛站股價在2月1日、2日出現顯著下跌，比上一周的最高價下降超過80%。2月2日，遊戲驛站股價跌幅高達60%，收盤價自1月25日以來首次低於100美元。其他發生軋空的股票，如AMC、黑莓也出現30%以上跌幅。這些股票的市值和最高點相比蒸發了270億美元<ref name="FT 210202">{{cite news |last1=Platt |first1=Eric |display-authors=etal |title=GameStop shares plunge as Reddit rally deflates |url=https://www.ft.com/content/1be70d9a-91d5-4cbb-a174-37d7b52b6af2 |access-date=2021-02-02 |work=Financial Times |date=2021-02-02}}</ref><ref name="Bloom 210202">{{cite news |last1=Lipschultz |first1=Bailey |title=GameStop Rout Erases $27 Billion as Reddit Favorites Lose Steam |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-02/gamestop-extends-pullback-with-short-interest-and-volume-sinking |access-date=2021-02-02 |work=Bloomberg News |date=2021-02-02}}</ref>。2月5日，GameStop又暴跌41.7%<ref>{{cite news |title=GameStop暴跌41% 道指再涨332点 标普纳指齐创新高 |url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2423185.html}}</ref>。

== 影響 ==
=== 對對沖基金的影響 ===
至1月28日，做空遊戲驛站的對沖基金[[梅爾文資本|梅爾文資本]]在2021年已損失了其30%的市值<ref name="GuardianWhiteHouseMonitoring" />。在梅爾文資本於1月26日在[[CNBC|CNBC]]上表示已平倉全部頭寸（但未公佈具體數額）之前<ref name="CNBCMelvinClosed" /><ref name="WSJMelvinBillion" />，城堡公司和其合作方對梅爾文資本進行20億美元的融資。{{link-en|Point72資產管理公司|Point72 Asset Management}}亦對梅爾文資本融資7.5億美元，雙方累積融資27.5億美元<ref name="chung">{{Cite news|last=Chung|first=Juliet|date=2021-01-25|title=WSJ News Exclusive {{!}} Citadel, Point72 to Invest $2.75 Billion Into Melvin Capital Management|language=en-US|work=Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/citadel-point72-to-invest-2-75-billion-into-melvin-capital-management-11611604340|access-date=2021-01-25|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128233028/https://www.wsj.com/articles/citadel-point72-to-invest-2-75-billion-into-melvin-capital-management-11611604340}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=McCabe|first=Caitlin|date=2021-01-14|title=GameStop Stock Soars, and Social-Media Traders Claim Victory|language=en-US|work=Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/gamestop-stock-soars-and-social-media-traders-claim-victory-11610653679|access-date=2021-01-23|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127043245/https://www.wsj.com/articles/gamestop-stock-soars-and-social-media-traders-claim-victory-11610653679}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Chung|first=Juliet|date=2021-01-22|title=WSJ News Exclusive {{!}} Short Bets Pummel Hot Hedge Fund Melvin Capital|language=en-US|work=Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/short-bets-pummel-hot-hedge-fund-melvin-capital-11611349217|access-date=2021-01-23|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127140132/https://www.wsj.com/articles/short-bets-pummel-hot-hedge-fund-melvin-capital-11611349217}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-01-25|title=Ken Griffin's $2 billion bet|url=https://www.chicagobusiness.com/finance-banking/ken-griffins-2-billion-bet|access-date=2021-01-25|website=Crain's Chicago Business|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126210146/https://www.chicagobusiness.com/finance-banking/ken-griffins-2-billion-bet}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Citadel, Point72 Back Melvin With $2.75 Billion After Losses|url=https://finance.yahoo.com/news/citadel-point72-back-melvin-2-203509666.html|access-date=2021-01-28|website=finance.yahoo.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126024053/https://finance.yahoo.com/news/citadel-point72-back-melvin-2-203509666.html}}</ref>。據信另一家做空遊戲驛站的對沖基金香橼研究在這次事件中虧損100%，被迫平倉<ref name="BloombergHowWallStreetBets" /><ref name="BuzzFeedAngryMob" />。據[[摩根士丹利|摩根士丹利]]表示，大量對沖基金補倉了它們的空頭頭寸，並出售股票以降低[[資金槓桿|槓桿]]率和市場風險，其規模是過去10年最大<ref name="AutoFB-7"/>。2021年1月26日，有報道稱空方在這次軋空損失50.5億美元<ref name="ShortsightDown5Billion"/>。

據Ortex數據的調查顯示，至1月27日，有超過5,000家美國做市商有虧損的空方頭寸<ref>{{cite news |last1=Rao |first1=Sujata |title=Losses on short positions in U.S. firms top $70 billion - Ortex data |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-retail-trading-shortbets-idUSKBN29X1SW?taid=6012f37e9ac87d000147d4e3 |work=Reuters |date=2021-01-28 |language=en |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129010501/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-retail-trading-shortbets-idUSKBN29X1SW?taid=6012f37e9ac87d000147d4e3  }}</ref>。

香橼研究的安德魯·萊夫特在一次採訪中表示，該公司以每股90美元的價格平倉了大部分做空頭寸，虧損率100%，現在僅持有少量可控頭寸<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-01-27|title=An update from Citron Research|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yS4yPsmaDDQ|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129090141/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yS4yPsmaDDQ}}</ref>。由於巨額損失，萊夫特表示香橼研究今後將停止提供做空分析，而集中精力在「為散戶提供做多機會」<ref>{{Cite web|last=Crabill|first=Steven|date=2021-01-29|title=Citron halts 20 years of short-sell analysis after GameStop woes Bloomberg|url=https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/citron-halts-20-years-of-short-sell-analysis-after-gamestop-woes-1.1556108|access-date=2021-01-30|website=BNN Bloomberg|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129171450/https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/citron-halts-20-years-of-short-sell-analysis-after-gamestop-woes-1.1556108}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-01-29|title=【GME事件】香櫞宣布不再發表沽空報告|url=https://hktecmedia.com/gmecitronresearchfail/|website=hkTec|date=2021-02-05|}}</ref>。

據《華爾街日報》報道，萊夫特成為[[網絡暴力|網絡暴力]]的標的，包括他本人的社交媒體賬戶被駭客入侵，他的子女也被「侮辱性詞彙威脅」<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Zuckerman|first1=Gregory|last2=Rogow|first2=Geoffrey|date=2021-01-27|title=The GameStop Short Squeeze Shows an Ugly Side of the Investing World|language=en-US|work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/gamestop-stock-short-squeeze-ugly-side-11611750250|access-date=2021-01-27|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127142123/https://www.wsj.com/articles/gamestop-stock-short-squeeze-ugly-side-11611750250}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=GameStop short-sellers Melvin Capital and Citron surrender their bearish bets after 700% rally drives huge losses|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/gamestop-stock-short-sellers-melvin-capital-citron-surrender-bets-gme-2021-1|date=2021-01-27|last=Winck|first=Ben|access-date=2021-01-27|website=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]]|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130044530/https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/gamestop-stock-short-sellers-melvin-capital-citron-surrender-bets-gme-2021-1-1030010382}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Citron Research covered majority of GameStop short position in $90s/share|url=https://seekingalpha.com/news/3654791-citron-research-covered-majority-of-gamestop-short-position-in-90sshare|access-date=2021-01-27|website=Seeking Alpha|last=Fineman|first=Josh|date=2021-01-27|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127115643/https://seekingalpha.com/news/3654791-citron-research-covered-majority-of-gamestop-short-position-in-90sshare}}</ref>。

據{{link-en|IHS Markit|IHS Markit}}數據，遊戲驛站的做空股對流通股的比例從1月中旬的114%下降至2月1日的39%。彭博社分析稱「這可能是空頭平倉的早期徵兆」<ref>{{cite news |title=GameStop Short Interest Plunges in Sign Traders Are Covering |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-01/gamestop-short-interest-plummets-in-a-sign-traders-are-covering |last1=Greifeld |first1=Katherine |last2=Wang |first2=Lu |work=[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]] |date=2021-02-01 |language=en |access-date=2021-02-01}}</ref>。

=== 對被軋空企業的影響 ===
自1月1日開始，黑莓和遊戲驛站的高管已售出超過2,200萬美元的公司股票<ref name=CBSFrenzy />。據[[CBS新聞|CBS新聞]]的報道，並無針對黑莓高管的[[內線交易|內線交易]]指控<ref name=CBSFrenzy />。三名黑莓高管出售了近170萬美元的公司股票。黑莓的[[首席財務官|首席財務官]]（CFO）斯蒂夫·賴（Steve Rai）出售他持有的公司股份（不含未歸屬的員工認股權）<ref name=CBSFrenzy>{{Cite web|title=Corporate executives reap millions from Reddit stock frenzy|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/reddit-stocks-wallstreet-bets-executive-payday/|last=Gandel|first=Stephen|date=2021-01-30|access-date=2021-01-31|website=[[CBS_News|CBS News]]|language=en-US}}</ref>。

自2021年開始，遊戲驛站董事會的四名成員已賣出了2,000萬美元的公司股票。賣方之一是庫爾特·沃爾夫（Kurt Wolf），他在2020年加入董事會<ref name=CBSFrenzy />。他的投資基金Hestia Capital於1月出售了其在遊戲驛站持有的三分之二以上股份，沃爾夫和其客戶因此獲得超過1,700萬美元<ref name=CBSFrenzy />。遊戲驛站董事長凱西·弗拉貝克（Kathy Vrabeck）和董事會成員勞爾·費南德斯（Raul Fernandez）在1月13日至1月16日出售了股票，獲利140萬美元。董事會成員利扎貝斯·邓恩也通過出售股票而獲得15.67萬美元<ref name=CBSFrenzy /><ref>{{Cite web|last=Lin|first=Ed|title=GameStop Insiders Sold Stock Before It Went Vertical|url=https://www.barrons.com/articles/gamestop-insiders-sold-stock-before-it-went-vertical-51611760507|date=2021-01-27|access-date=2021-01-31|website=Barron's|language=en-US}}</ref>。據[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]報道，遊戲驛站CEO喬治·謝爾曼（George Sherman）擁有230萬股的公司股票。他的股票市值從12月31日的4,400萬美元開始升高。當遊戲驛站股價達469美元時，其所有的股票市值達11億美元，令謝爾曼一度成為億萬富翁。但在1月29日，由於股價下跌，他所有的股票市值也減少至9.01億美元<ref>{{Cite web|title=GameStop CEO’s shares are worth nearly $1 billion—and, boy, does he probably want to sell|url=https://fortune.com/2021/01/29/gamestop-stock-ceo-george-sherman-gme-shares-net-worth-billion/|date=2021-01-29|last=Lambert|first=Lance|access-date=2021-01-31|website=[[Fortune_(magazine)|Fortune]]|language=en}}</ref>。據CBS新聞報道，遊戲驛站已採取行動，限制高層和內部人士出售更多股份。但由於相關事件都是因外部消息和公眾猜測發生，高管們並未違反內線交易法律<ref name=CBSFrenzy />。
==== 既有股東和第三方的獲利 ====
據[[路透社|路透社]]的分析，在這起事件中，華爾街的一些大型資產管理公司因他們的持股及將持股外借給空方獲利<ref name="reutersreport">{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-retail-trading-funds-analysis/analysis-how-wall-street-gains-from-populist-trading-movement-idUSKBN29Y0I4|title=Analysis: How Wall Street gains from 'populist' trading movement|first=Ross |last=Kerber|date=2021-01-29|website=Reuters}}</ref>。券商、交易系統、做市商也從交易者高於平時的交易量獲利<ref name="reutersreport" />。

