=== 公眾人物 ===
Reddit的共同創始人之一在接受[[CNBC|CNBC]]訪問時將這一事件和[[佔領華爾街|佔領華爾街]]運動相比較，並表示「這是{{link-en|典型平均美国人|Average Joe}}——散戶投資者對對沖基金的報復」<ref name="MarketWatchOccupyReddit"/>。眾多記者也比較了這次事件和佔領華爾街運動<ref name="cheng"/><ref name="BloombergOccupy"/><ref name="evans"/>。億萬富翁投資家[[馬克·庫班|馬克·庫班]]<ref name="Auto9F-4" />和{{link-en|查馬斯·帕利哈皮蒂亞|Chamath Palihapitiya}}也表達了類似的同情散戶的意見<ref name="chamath">{{Cite tweet|link=https://twitter.com/chamath/status/1354947541125611526|number=1354947541125611526|user=chamath|title=I remember when I met the @RobinhoodApp founders when they were raising their Seed, Series A and Series B.  I passed. Why? Optimize for integrity whenever possible because integrity compounds and assholes will fuck you. #DeleteRobinhood|author=Chamath Palihapitiya|date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://archive.is/wITRz}}</ref>。帕利哈皮蒂亞放棄了他在羅賓漢的原始投資機會，認為其創始者{{link-en|拜居·巴哈特|Baiju Bhatt}}和{{link-en|弗拉基米爾·特內夫|Vladimir Tenev}}不夠正直，並鼓勵他的粉絲刪除羅賓漢<ref name="chamath" />。[[OpenAI|OpenAI]]的CEO{{link-en|山姆·奧特曼|Sam Altman}}建議羅賓漢公司更名<ref>{{Cite tweet|title=fuck robinhood must change name imo|date=2021-01-28|number=1354842339336835074|user=sama|author=Sam Altman|link=https://twitter.com/sama/status/1354842339336835074|archive-url=https://archive.is/tco6S|archive-date=2021-01-28|retweet=875}}</ref>。[[SpaceX|SpaceX]]和[[特斯拉_(公司)|特斯拉]]CEO[[伊隆·馬斯克|伊隆·馬斯克]]批評了做空行為本身，稱其是「歷史遺留的合法騙局」<ref name=":0">{{cite news |title=Elon Musk lashes out at short sellers during GameStop market war |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/elon-musk-short-sellers-gamestop-b1794444.html |work=The Independent |date=2021-01-28 |language=en |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129040712/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/elon-musk-short-sellers-gamestop-b1794444.html}}</ref>。多家大型對沖基金曾做空特斯拉，但因特斯拉股價持續上漲而損失超過400億美元<ref name=":0" />。

