=== 羅賓漢與城堡公司的利益衝突指控 ===
{{See also|Citadel LLC}}
在羅賓漢暫停投資者買入遊戲驛站及其他軋空股票後，Reddit和其他社交媒體用戶紛紛對羅賓漢和[[Citadel_LLC|城堡公司]]（Citadel LLC）之間的關係提出質疑<ref name="FT 210129" /><ref name="WaPo 210129">{{cite news |last1=MacMillan |first1=Douglas |last2=Torbati |first2=Yeganeh |title=Robinhood and Citadel’s relationship comes into focus as Washington vows to examine stock-market moves |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/2021/01/29/robinhood-citadel-gamestop-reddit/ |access-date=2021-01-30|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |date=2021-01-29}}</ref><ref name="FoxBus 210128">{{cite news |last1=Garber |first1=Jonathan |title=Citadel shoots down Robinhood link |url=https://www.foxbusiness.com/markets/citadel-shoots-down-robinhood-link |access-date=2021-01-30 |work=Fox Business |date=2021-01-28}}</ref>。據彭博社早前報道，羅賓漢40%的收入來自於將客戶訂單銷售給[[做市商|做市商]]，包括[[Citadel_LLC|城堡公司]]和[[Two_Sigma|Two Sigma]]，這種做法被稱為{{link-en|訂單流支付|payment for order flow}}<ref name="BloombergRobinhoodControversial"/>。《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》報道稱，羅賓漢將其半數以上的客戶訂單賣給城堡公司，城堡公司是其金額最大的做市夥伴<ref name="WaPo 210129" />。城堡證券（Citadel Securities ）是城堡公司（Citadel LLC）的姊妹公司，而城堡公司是梅爾文資本的注資方之一<ref name="chung"/>。由於羅賓漢限制遊戲驛站股票交易，抑制股價上漲。因此用戶聲稱羅賓漢的這一行為是來自於城堡證券的指示。城堡證券則聲稱他們並未指示任何券商暫停或以其它方式限制股票交易。羅賓漢亦否認受到來自城堡公司的壓力<ref name="FT 210129" /><ref name="WaPo 210129" /><ref name="FoxBus 210128" /><ref>{{Cite web |last=Fitzgerald |first=Maggie |date=January 28, 2021 |title=Robinhood restricts trading in GameStop, other names involved in frenzy |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/28/robinhood-interactive-brokers-restrict-trading-in-gamestop-s.html  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129003245/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/28/robinhood-interactive-brokers-restrict-trading-in-gamestop-s.html |archive-date=2021-01-29|access-date=2021-01-28|website=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |language=en}}</ref>。

