=== 訴訟 ===
一位羅賓漢用戶對羅賓漢提起[[集體訴訟|集體訴訟]]，聲稱羅賓漢「蓄意在其交易平台刪除遊戲驛站股票，導致散戶無法在公開市場上投資」；並認為羅賓漢停止遊戲驛站股票交易的行為是「蓄意操縱市場的嘗試，以為非羅賓漢客戶的個人或金融機構謀取利益」<ref name="CNNRobinhoodClassAction" /><ref name="The Hill 210128">{{cite news |last1=Mills Rodrigo |first1=Chris |title=Class-action lawsuit filed against Robinhood for restricting trading |url=https://thehill.com/policy/healthcare/536320-class-action-lawsuit-filed-against-robinhood-for-restricting-trading |access-date=2021-01-29|work=[[The_Hill_(newspaper)|The Hill]] |date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128203812/https://thehill.com/policy/healthcare/536320-class-action-lawsuit-filed-against-robinhood-for-restricting-trading }}</ref>。提起訴訟的律師亞歷山大·G·卡被塞拉斯（Alexander G. Cabeceiras）發推文稱「羅賓漢聲稱自己的目標是對所有人實現金融民主化，這顯然是謊言」<ref name="Hodjat" />。該訴訟已提交至[[美國紐約南區聯邦地區法院|美國紐約南區聯邦地區法院]]，要求恢復該平台上的遊戲驛站交易，並要求羅賓漢負擔集體訴訟費、律師費、懲罰性賠償<ref name="Auto9F-1" />。亦有多位投資人通過app{{link-en|DoNotPay|DoNotPay}}自動加入訴訟<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/29/app-robinhood-gamestop-class-action-lawsuit.html |title= Investors are using this app to automatically join the Robinhood class-action lawsuit amid GameStop chaos |date=2021-01-29|last=Adamczyk |first=Alicia |website=[[NBC_News|NBC News]] |access-date=2021-01-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.vice.com/en/article/akdaj5/join-robinhood-class-action-lawsuit |title=This App Lets You Automatically Join the Robinhood Class Action Lawsuit |date=2021-01-28 |last=Cox |first=Joseph |website=Vice |access-date=2021-01-30}}</ref>。

