由於券商停止散戶購入遊戲驛站和其他相關股票，資金轉向加密貨幣市場。加密貨幣的總市值增加至超過1萬億美元，尤以[[多吉幣|多吉幣]]漲幅最高，超過800%<ref>{{Cite web |last=Cuthbertson |first=Anthony |date=2021-01-29 |title=GameStop frenzy takes cryptocurrency market over $1 trillion |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/dogecoin-price-stock-buy-gamestop-reddit-bitcoin-b1794695.html |website=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129144052/https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/dogecoin-price-stock-buy-gamestop-reddit-bitcoin-b1794695.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/29/dogecoin-cryptocurrency-rises-over-400percent-after-reddit-group-talks-it-up.html |title=Reddit frenzy pumps up Dogecoin, a cryptocurrency started as a joke, by over 800% |date=January 28, 2021 |last=Kharpal |first=Arjun |website=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |access-date=2021-01-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/billybambrough/2021/01/28/after-robinhood-restricts-gamestop-bitcoin-and-crypto-market-suddenly-soars-toward-1-trillion-dogecoin-rockets-200/ |title=After Robinhood Restricts GameStop, Bitcoin And Crypto Market Suddenly Soars Toward $1 Trillion—Dogecoin Price Rockets 200% |date=January 28, 2021 |last=Bambrough |first=Bill |website=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |access-date=2021-01-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.avclub.com/the-gamestop-stonk-bubble-has-swallowed-dogecoin-frank-1846150526 |title=The GameStop stonk bubble has swallowed DogeCoin, Frankie Muniz |date=2021-01-29 |last=Paul |first=Andrew |website=[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]] |access-date=2021-01-29}}</ref>。Reddit上r/CryptoCurrency和r/SatoshiStreetBets的用戶試圖將多吉幣「成為下一個遊戲驛站/比特幣」<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/roberthart/2021/01/28/its-doge-time-dogecoin-surges-as-reddit-traders-push-to-make-it-the-crypto-gamestop/ |title='It’s Doge Time': Dogecoin Surges As Reddit Traders Push To Make It The Crypto GameStop |date=2021-01-29 |last=Hart |first=Robert |website=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |access-date=2021-01-29}}</ref>。此外在伊隆·馬斯克於他的推特中支持[[比特幣|比特幣]]之後，世界最大的加密貨幣比特幣價格也上揚至超過37,000美元。這也和遊戲驛站軋空有關<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/29/bitcoin-spikes-20percent-after-elon-musk-adds-bitcoin-to-his-twitter-bio.html |title=Bitcoin spikes 20% after Elon Musk adds #bitcoin to his Twitter bio |first=Ryan |last=Browne |date=2021-01-29 |website=CNBC |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129102120/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/29/bitcoin-spikes-20percent-after-elon-musk-adds-bitcoin-to-his-twitter-bio.html }}</ref>。

=== 金屬期貨 ===
繼股市飆升之後，[[銀|白銀]]期貨也出現井噴<ref name=CNBCSilver>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/31/silver-futures-jump-7percent-as-reddit-traders-try-their-squeeze-play-with-the-metal.html |title=Silver futures jump 7% as Reddit traders try their squeeze play with the metal |date=2021-01-31 |last=Pound |first=Jesse |website=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |access-date=2021-01-31}}</ref><ref name=BloombergSilver />。1月28日至29日，白銀價格上漲10%<ref>{{Cite news|last=Rao|first=Svea Herbst-Bayliss, Sujata|date=2021-01-31|title=Wall Street gears up for second bout against Reddit traders|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-retail-trading-idUSKBN2A00UH|access-date=2021-02-01}}</ref>。白銀[[指數股票型基金|ETF]]在1月28日上漲7.2％。白銀關聯股票{{link-en|First Majestic Silver|First Majestic Silver}}亦出現飆升<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/reddit-day-traders-silver-next-short-squeeze-2021-1-1030017108 |title=Reddit day traders look to silver as the next short-squeeze after being restricted from hot stocks |first=Will |last=Daniel |date=2021-01-28 |website=Markets Insider |access-date=2021-01-31 |archive-date=2021-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131122755/https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/reddit-day-traders-silver-next-short-squeeze-2021-1-1030017108 }}</ref>。[[倫敦金屬交易所|倫敦金屬交易所]]的[[黃金|黃金]]和[[銅|銅]]的價格也出現上漲<ref name=BloombergSilver>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-28/silver-is-the-latest-market-hit-by-reddit-day-trader-frenzy |title=Silver Is the Latest Market Hit by Reddit Day-Trader Frenzy |date=2021-01-28 |last1=Yue Li |first1=Yvonne |last2=Deaux |first2=Joe |website=[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]] |access-date=2021-01-31}}</ref>。1月30日，Reddit有用戶表示，白銀價格被低估，應大幅買入白銀。2月1日，由於遊戲驛站股價繼續劇烈波動，白银期货价格大涨约11%，創下2009年以来最大单日涨幅<ref>{{cite news |title=Reddit散户涌向白银是市场疯狂的又一征兆 |url=https://cn.wsj.com/articles/reddit%E6%95%A3%E6%88%B7%E6%B6%8C%E5%90%91%E7%99%BD%E9%93%B6%E6%98%AF%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E7%96%AF%E7%8B%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%88%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%BE%81%E5%85%86-11612236014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=散户大举买入推动银价暴涨至八年最高 金价跳升1% |url=https://cn.reuters.com/article/precious-metals-0201-mon-idCNKBS2A200K}}</ref>，白銀的價格也創出8年新高<ref>{{cite web |last1=Wearden |first1=Graeme |last2=Sweney |first2=Mark |title=Silver price hits eight-year high, as GameStop shares fall back – business live |url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/live/2021/feb/01/silver-price-squeeze-reddit-traders-gamestop-ftse-dow-uk-factories-business-live |website=The Guardian |date=2021-02-01}}</ref>。但r/wallstreetbets的用戶否認參與白銀價格炒作<ref>{{cite news |last1=Morris |first1=Chris |title=Reddit users say they are not behind Monday’s silver squeeze |url=https://fortune.com/2021/02/01/silver-price-slv-wallstreetbets-reddit-gamestop-short-squeeze-latest-commodities/ |access-date=2021-02-01 |publisher=fortune,com |date=2021-02-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Ferre |first1=Ines |title=Redditors divided on shift to push up Silver |url=https://finance.yahoo.com/news/silver-to-the-moon-says-redditor-but-others-on-wall-street-bets-differ-160221386.html |access-date=2021-02-01 |publisher=finance.yahoo.org |date=2021-02-01}}</ref>，並稱白銀價格上升的原因是城堡公司等持有白銀頭寸的機構和對沖基金，以抵消它們在遊戲驛站上的虧損<ref>{{Cite news|title=Hi ho silver! Online investors push up price of precious metal as market volatility continues {{!}} CBC News|language=en-US|work=CBC|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/silver-stocks-surge-1.5895790|access-date=2021-02-01}}</ref>。

